Heya Hi2grils,

The refund button is located in settings. To get there you have to go to the store; in the upper right corner below your RP and IP values you should see a cog. Click the cog to go to account settings. On the left side of the screen you should see an option for purchase history. Once you go to your purchase history you should be able to refund like normal.

